TITLE: Reproducible Nix Shell Script for Fetching and Formatting GitHub Releases
DESCRIPTION: A reproducible script using nix-shell as interpreter with explicitly declared dependencies. It fetches Nixpkgs releases as XML, converts to JSON, and formats the output with jq. The script pins the exact version of Nixpkgs to ensure consistent behavior across systems.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nixos/nix.dev/blob/master/source/tutorials/first-steps/reproducible-scripts.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
#!/usr/bin/env nix-shell
#! nix-shell -i bash --pure
#! nix-shell -p bash cacert curl jq python3Packages.xmljson
#! nix-shell -I nixpkgs=https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/archive/2a601aafdc5605a5133a2ca506a34a3a73377247.tar.gz

curl https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/releases.atom | xml2json | jq .
```

