TITLE: Creating a Basic shell.nix File in Nix
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a basic shell.nix file that defines a shell environment with cowsay and lolcat packages. It uses a pinned version of Nixpkgs and the mkShellNoCC function to create the environment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nixos/nix.dev/blob/master/source/tutorials/first-steps/declarative-shell.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

