TITLE: Sharing Dependencies between default.nix and shell.nix in Nix
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the inputsFrom attribute in default.nix to share package dependencies with shell.nix. It defines a build attribute and a shell attribute that inherits the build's dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nixos/nix.dev/blob/master/source/guides/recipes/sharing-dependencies.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: nix
CODE:
```
# default.nix
let
  pkgs = import <nixpkgs> {};
  build = pkgs.callPackage ./build.nix {};
in
{
  inherit build;
  shell = pkgs.mkShellNoCC {
    inputsFrom = [ build ];
  };
}
```

