TITLE: Configuring a Cross-Compilation Environment in Nix
DESCRIPTION: A shell.nix configuration that sets up an environment for cross-compiling to aarch64 architecture with static binaries using musl. It configures the necessary build tools and libraries for the target platform.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nixos/nix.dev/blob/master/source/tutorials/cross-compilation.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: nix
CODE:
```
